  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add them to a pot with plenty of water and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 15 min or until fork-tender</p>",
