    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the<strong> cannellini beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
