            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>diced onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3 min or until softened</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
