          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, the <strong>apple</strong> <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong>, then crumble in the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong>,</span> stir and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-low, cook for 10 min, then add the drained <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Keep on a low heat until serving</p>",
      "order": 4,
