      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, once cooked, drain and run the <strong>potatoes</strong> under <strong>cold water</strong> until cool enough to handle</p><p>Return to the pot and mash until smooth</p><p>Add half of the <strong>chopped chives </strong>(save the rest for later!), 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, season generously and mix</p>",
